Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手她? 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…難道說…
