Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:56.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(779,652)}時空境界的教理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 正好放在一樓的42寸顯像管電視機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發揮了Lifter的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有在修理店營業 電視機開著的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能發送D-MAIL嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確說得通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊得我頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.顯像管這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會暴力相向…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這就是活該
